creator: ShareDesk Global Inc
descriptionHtml:
Now you can access the exciting co-working opportunities and benefits offered by ACS Labs â whether it is River City Labs in Brisbane, Harbour City Labs in Sydney, or Bay City Labs in Melbourne â all in one place through a single, interactive app.

Download the ACS Labs app today and connect with the accelerator and startup community that makes up the River City Labs, Bay City Labs, and Harbour City Labs co-working digital spaces. See the co-working space in action, book a room, check into any of the Labs and more!
descriptionShort: ACS Labs is a workplace management app that provides interactive benefits.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Bug fixes
- We’ve made a number of improvements to invoicing including the ability to pay pending invoice before end of the billing cycle.
- You can now open community feed photos in full screen and then save it to your gallery app.
